## ⚙️ CẤU HÌNH VS CODE LAUNCH.JSON (Debug)

### **Tạo file .vscode/launch.json**
```json
{
    "version": "0.2.0",
    "configurations": [
        {
            "name": "Launch Backend",
            "type": "php",
            "request": "launch",
            "port": 9000,
            "pathMappings": {
                "/var/www/html": "${workspaceFolder}/backend"
            }
        },
        {
            "name": "Launch Frontend",
            "type": "chrome",
            "request": "launch",
            "url": "http://localhost:5173",
            "webRoot": "${workspaceFolder}/frontend"
        },
        {
            "name": "Launch Realtime",
            "type": "node",
            "request": "launch",
            "cwd": "${workspaceFolder}/realtime",
            "runtimeExecutable": "npm",
            "runtimeArgs": ["run", "dev"]
        }
    ],
    "compounds": [
        {
            "name": "Launch All",
            "configurations": ["Launch Backend", "Launch Frontend", "Launch Realtime"]
        }
    ]
}
```


